parcel.name: CryptoHamsters Club
parcel.label: club
parcel.description:
CryptoHamsters are composed of DNA with 18 genetic instructions, generated randomly.

🐹 🚀

Create your team and be prepared!

### **SOCIAL NETWORKS**

 [Twitter](https://twitter.com/cryptohamsters_) • [Instagram](https://www.instagram.com/cryptohamsters/)

Join the [Discord](https://discord.gg/cryptohamsters)  and live the community, especially if you already have a hamster.

Be sure to visit the **[Hamsterverse](https://lynkfire.com/CryptoHamsters)** to stay up to date.
